# GitHub Issue Tracking

## Before starting work
```bash
gh issue view PM-XXX  # Verify issue exists
```

## During work
- Update issue descriptions (not comments)
- Check boxes as tasks complete
- Provide evidence links

## Issue creation
```bash
# Check next number in CSV
tail -5 docs/planning/pm-issues-status.csv
```

See github-guide.md for full operations.
